title: The Dirty Lies - Release EP (FLAC) (2014)
description:
Leeds (England) based band 'The Dirty Lies', and their first EP, 'Release'.



'The darkly subdued sounds of The Dirty Lies float around the room in a contemplative mood as the quartet combine instrumentation and synthetics to deliver music laden with atmosphere.'



If you enjoy this, consider supporting the band by purchasing a hard copy from 

www.electriccompanymusic.com
